quran[15{c,v,t}:
50,1,"q, qasam hai quran Majeed ki"
50,2,"balkay inn logon ko taajjub is baat par howa ke aik khabardaar karne wala khud aِnhi mein se inn ke paas agaya phir munkareen kehnay lagey"" yeh to ajeeb baat hai"
50,3,"kya jab hum mar jayen ge aur khaak ho jayen ge ( to dobarah uthaye jayen ge )? yeh wapsi to aqal se baeed hai """
50,4,zameen un ke jism mein se jo kuch khati hai woh sab hamaray ilm mein hai aur hamaray paas aik kitaab hai jis mein sab kuch mehfooz hai
50,5,balkay inn logon ne to jis waqt haq inn ke paas aaya usi waqt ussay saaf jhutla diya isi wajah se ab yeh uljan mein parre hue hain
50,6,"acha, to kya unhon ne kabhi apne oopar aasman ki taraf nahi dekha? kis terhan hum ne usay banaya aur aaraasta kya, aur is mein kahin koi rakhna nahi hai"
50,7,aur zameen ko hum ne bichhaya aur is mein pahar jamaye aur uss ke andar har terhan ki khush manzar nabataat uga den
50,8,yeh saari cheeze ankhen kholnay wali aur sabaq dainay wali hain har uss bande ke liye jo ( haq ki taraf ) rujoo karne wala ho
50,9,"aur aasman se hum ne barket wala pani nazil kya, phir is se baagh aur fasal ke ghallay"
50,10,aur buland o baala khajoor ke darakht peda kar diye jin par phalon se lde hue khoshay teh Bar teh lagtay hain
50,11,yeh intizam hai bundon ko rizaq dainay ka iss pani se hum aik murda zameen ko zindagi bakhash dete hain ( marey hue insanon ka zameen se ) niklana bhi isi terhan ho ga
50,12,"inn se pehlay Nooh ki qoum, aur ashaab alras aur smod"
50,13,"aur Aad , aur firaon, aur loot ke bhai"
50,14,"aur ایکہ walay, aur tba ki qoum ke log bhi jhutla chuke hain har aik ne Rasolo-n ko jhtlaya, aur aakhir-kaar meri vayd unn par chaspan ho gayi"
50,15,kya pehli baar ki takhleeq se hum aajiz thay? magar aik nai takhleeq ki taraf se yeh log shak mein parre hue hain
